| Tuesday | 102 | 2.3s | $0.31 | 0 |
| Wednesday | 98 | 2.2s | $4.82 | 0 |
| Thursday | 110 | 3.8s | $0.33 | 3 |
| Friday | 88 | 8.5s | $0.27 | 12 |

Additional detail:
